Take a walkthrough and enjoy the unique interior on this sportfish!

This boat was listed by @galatiyachtsales last year with an asking price of $2,595,000⁣ 
⁣
This enclosed bridge yacht features 3 Staterooms, 3 Head, Crew Quarter and Head layout. A U-shaped seating in the large Salon with powered day/night blinds, Galley and Dinette with granite countertops, white oak floors, wine cooler.⁣ ⁣

node.text:
Family Circus” is a head turner everywhere she goes, powered with twin 1000hp CAT C12.9’s which provide a speedy cruise yet does so efficiently and comfortably. This 46 WA was built for a true yachtsman who loves to fish and travel around the Bahamas, make no mistake this vessel does it well. Her deck features a full walkaround layout without steps or obstacles when navigating from bow to stern which comes in handy when fighting that fish of a lifetime, entertaining or setting lines. “Family Circus” is outfitted and optioned with more features than you would typically find on a 60’+ sportfish, some notable features include; Seakeeper 6, Spot Zero System, Water Maker, Eskimo Ice Maker, Aux Oil Reservoir, Hydraulic Outriggers, Custom Built-In Teak Furniture, Helm Deck Air Conditioning, Faux Painted Toe Rail and Transom, Bow Thruster, FLIR and so much more! See full specs for the full list of equipment and options. CONTACT Mordy @miltzmaritime @united_yacht_sales
